data.description: FLEXIBLE OWNER FINANCING - 10-15% DOWN ONLY and 7% INTEREST.  Step into a haven of brightness and spacious elegance in the coveted Hollywood Park gardens. Bask in natural light amidst tall ceilings and a free-flowing layout. Your culinary journey starts in a kitchen adorned with Silestone counters, a brand-new oven, and distinct dining spaces. Retreat to the master suite, complete with direct outdoor access, a luxurious garden tub, and a walk-in closet fit for royalty. Cozy up by the fireplace in the expansive living area or step outside to a serene patio - perfect for gatherings in a private backyard. The community boasts unmatched amenities: 3 pools, splash pad, state-of-the-art amenity center, sand volleyball, full-sized basketball court, a whimsical butterfly garden, and direct access for Sonterra golf cart enthusiasts. Don't miss out on this gem!
